Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter's visits fail to ignite campaign
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w2nz
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 15 Jun 1980
President Carter's flying visits to crisis-torn areas seen only as political and fail to boost his standing. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less